alf believing it, she decides to hang around with Keishi. Later, with the help of Sawaki, a detective she knows, the stalker is identified. She thinks the case is closed but a totally unexpected person attacks her...","genre_ids":[28,80,53],"popularity":0.2404,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/7V32EqGrJ4CAHNk4xMx55VXTWM9.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-28","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"6時間後に君は死ぬ","original_language":"ja"},{"id":470894,"adult":false,"title":"At First Light","video":false,"overview":"High school senior Alex has an encounter with mysterious lights that appear over her small town. She soon develops dangerous, supernatural abilities, and turns to her childhood friend Sean. The authorities target them and a chase ensues as officials try to discover the truth behind Alex's transformation.","genre_ids":[53,878],"popularity":1.2167,"vote_count":143,"poster_path":"/wez4hCV7ltekZwRkQVyiKEZNrm5.jpg","release_date":"2018-10-05","vote_average":5.7,"backdrop_path":"/rexivjdRPxvcqMFU1cHY3g1IaZa.jpg","original_title":"At First Light","original_language":"en"},{"id":8839,"adult":false,"title":"Casper","video":false,"overview":"Casper is a kind young ghost who peacefully haunts a mansion in Maine. When specialist James Harvey arrives to communicate with Casper and his fellow spirits, he brings along his teenage daughter, Kat. Casper quickly falls in love with Kat, but their budding relationship is complicated not only by his transparent state, but also by his troublemaking apparition uncles and their mischievous antics.","genre_ids":[14,35,10751],"popularity":5.7829,"vote_count":4859,"poster_path":"/2ah8fNJFZVU3vcXhU5xfAYi2eym.jpg","release_date":"1995-05-26","vote_average":6.335,"backdrop_path":"/sQPckU0TfSeYIlUneHfIXwzQC2f.jpg","original_title":"Casper","original_language":"en"},{"id":8973,"adult":false,"title":"Lord of Illusions","video":false,"overview":"During a routine case in L.A., NY private investigator Harry D'Amour stumbles over members 