e,"title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","video":false,"overview":"During World War II, Steve Rogers is a sickly man from Brooklyn who's transformed into super-soldier Captain America to aid in the war effort. Rogers must stop the Red Skull – Adolf Hitler's ruthless head of weaponry, and the leader of an organization that intends to use a mysterious device of untold powers for world domination.","genre_ids":[28,12,878],"popularity":7.3077,"vote_count":22477,"poster_path":"/vSNxAJTlD0r02V9sPYpOjqDZXUK.jpg","release_date":"2011-07-22","vote_average":7.004,"backdrop_path":"/yFuKvT4Vm3sKHdFY4eG6I4ldAnn.jpg","original_title":"Captain America: The First Avenger","original_language":"en"},{"id":2154,"adult":false,"title":"The Dark Side of the Moon","video":false,"overview":"It is the year 2022. A mysterious systems failure causes the crew of a spaceship to be stranded on the dark side of the moon, while rapidly running out of fuel and oxygen. They are surprised to discover a NASA space shuttle floating in space, and board it in the hope of salvaging some supplies. One by one, the crew is possessed and killed, and it is up to Paxton Warner to find the links between the dark side of the moon, the Bermuda Triangle, and the Devil himself.","genre_ids":[27,28,53,878],"popularity":0.4739,"vote_count":90,"poster_path":"/etnsPUDbgbMGna2hiuRvHDx0xyz.jpg","release_date":"1990-05-30","vote_average":4.967,"backdrop_path":"/tPVphtpJtuHTC7vLsc71R0DmTLr.jpg","original_title":"The Dark Side of the Moon","original_language":"en"},{"id":1069108,"adult":false,"title":"Microwave Coven","video":false,"overview":"After buying a microwave from a peculiar woman, two college roommates discover their new appliance is not quite what it seems.","genre_ids":[35,27,14],"popularity":0.5034,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":"/oXC0suIkn6GiyDaBj7h0AUzunKA.jpg","release_date":"2023-07-27","vote_average":10,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Microwave Coven","original_language":"en"},{"id":279087,"adult":false,"title":"Specter","video":false,"overview":"The town of Midground is threatened by a tsunami caused by a massive earthquake in the North Pacific Ocean. After other unexplainable events transpire, Chase Lombardi and friends are forced to discover whether they are experiencing a natural phenomenon or something else all together.","genre_ids":[53,27,878],"popularity":1.3996,"vote_count":10,"poster_path":"/je0498EYKg39euyvu0ZvRmD8jhk.jpg","release_date":"2014-09-09","vote_average":3.6,"backdrop_path":"/u5qbQIk9SxvVFz3hiBGbbvJnT59.jpg","original_title":"Specter","original_language":"en"},{"id":1069813,"adult":false,"title":"Rohan at the Louvre","video":false,"overview":"Rohan Kishibe is a mangaka who can read people like a book. At work on a new creation, Rohan recalls a tale of the blackest painting ever made. Called the most evil of paintings, it used a paint that should not exist. Driven by the events linked to it, Rohan and his editor, Izumi, go to the Louvre in France for answers.","genre_ids":[9648,28,12,18],"popularity":0.4979,"vote_count":16,"poster_path":"/bweM7e0WinLaytxwIlARBRaeY7L.jpg","release_date":"2023-05-26","vote_average":7.875,"backdrop_path":"/iBfwwYQ15Gl2lf8j0yuuQnFiajg.jpg","original_title":"岸辺露伴 ルーヴルへ行く","original_language":"ja"},{"id":1461201,"adult":false,"title":"The Keeper of the Camphor Tree","video":false,"overview":"In Tokyo, left on his own after the loss of his mother and jobless, a series of bad decisions and misfortune lands young Reito in prison. Left with nothing, he has lost all hope for the future. But everything changes when a lawyer representing a powerful family empire offers him a way out—on one condition: he must take on a mysterious role as the Keeper of the Camphor Tree.","genre_ids":[16,18,9648,14],"popularity":0.6741,"vote_count":0,"poster_path":"/kvAG1owZk5JYrPZe8uYmsgodwBu.jpg","release_date":"2026-01-30","vote_average":0,"backdrop_path":"/iBCuy1Ic4BFuObMmMf4b7eGylqS.jpg","original_title":"クスノキの番人","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10072,"adult":false,"title":"A Nightmare on Elm Street 3: Dream Warriors","video":false,"overview":"A psychiatrist, familiar with the knife-wielding dream demon Freddy Krueger, helps teens at a mental hospital battle the killer who is invading their dreams.","genre_ids":[27,53,14],"popularity":1.7354,"vote_count":1971,"poster_path":"/qbtZewU6EGvxi8yFVzwZ31NijLX.jpg","release_date":"1987-02-27","vote_average":6.697,"backdrop_path":"/euXJlfeYSyrdkOoFQ9gtUG8OOhH.jpg","original_title":"A Nightmare on Elm Street 3: Dream Warriors","original_language":"en"},{"id":11596,"adult":false,"title":"New Nightmare","video":false,"overview":"A demonic force has chosen Freddy Krueger as its portal to the real world. Can Heather Langenkamp play the part of Nancy one last time and trap the evil trying to enter our world?","genre_ids":[27,9648,14],"popularity":2.0402,"vote_count":1545,"poster_path":"/eN3UZUYapJ2CJCD9dN0LUZLouKa.jpg","release_date":"1994-10-13","vote_average":6.462,"backdrop_path":"/qKF9GwtJbi2rob8kZBmGcQGAaMo.jpg","original_title":"New Nightmare","original_language":"en"},{"id":12187,"adult":false,"title":"Heart and Souls","video":false,"overview":"A fateful night in 1959, four people die when the bus they are riding crashes. They continue as ghosts; their souls become eternally entwined to the life of a child born at the moment of their deaths as his guardians. Baby Thomas grows up to be a businessman who has memories of his playmates, but assumes they are products of his youthful imagination. When the ghosts realize they need Thomas' help to move on to the afterlife, they decide to make an appearance once more.","genre_ids":[14,35,10749],"popularity":2.417,"vote_count":407,"poster_path":"/ik6GtJXMoq5tA581IMeBHr7Wocf.jpg","release_date":"1993-08-13","vote_average":6.889,"backdrop_path":"/orjpvbnfiDQvqRJIy9cLAb8WTgF.jpg","original_title":"Heart and Souls","original_language":"en"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt1343712","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":nu